title: Dakine Crossroads 32L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2014 Crossroads 32L Pack.
Features: 
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 17" laptops
- Front pocket fits iPad
- Breathable Dri Mesh back panel
- Blanket roll straps
- Fleece lined phone pocket
- Adjustable sternum strap
